org.apache.jackrabbit.oak.composite.checks

Interface MountedNodeStoreChecker<T>

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    NamespacePrefixNodestoreChecker, NodeTypeDefinitionNodeStoreChecker, NodeTypeMountedNodeStoreChecker, UniqueIndexNodeStoreChecker

    public interface MountedNodeStoreChecker<T>
    Applies a category of consistency checks specific to NodeStore mounts

    Checks are only performed on non-default mounts.

    Named 'Checker' to clarify that it is not a Validator in the Oak sense.
